{"article_id":"X7PvH7dqkUpwGUw6","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"CHICAGO -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"`` Empire '' actor Jussie Smollett plotted an attack","depth":9},{"id":2,"text":"to make himself look like the victim of a brutal anti-black , homophobic crime ,","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"prosecutors said Thursday .","depth":8},{"id":4,"text":"He scouted out the exact location with the two brothers","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"he paid","depth":11},{"id":6,"text":"to stage the hoax ,","depth":11},{"id":7,"text":"offered specific instructions","depth":11},{"id":8,"text":"on how he wanted to be beaten ,","depth":11},{"id":9,"text":"and even gave them $ 100","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"to buy supplies","depth":12},{"id":11,"text":"used in the staged assault ,","depth":12},{"id":12,"text":"prosecutors said .","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"The revelations came","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"as Smollett made his first court appearance Thursday afternoon at a bond hearing","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"following his early-morning arrest on a charge of disorderly conduct","depth":10},{"id":16,"text":"by filing a false police report .","depth":10},{"id":17,"text":"Judge John Fitzgerald Lyke Jr. set Smollett ' s bond at $ 100,000","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"and ordered him to surrender his passport .","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"No plea was entered","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"and the actor said little","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"other than giving his name .","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"Smollett posted bond late Thursday afternoon","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"and walked out of the Cook County Jail","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"without making comment to a phalanx of reporters .","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"Smollett ,","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"who is gay and black ,","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"told investigators","depth":9},{"id":28,"text":"he was beaten by two masked men","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"who shouted racial and homophobic slurs ,","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"wrapped a rope around his neck in the fashion of a noose","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"and poured bleach on him .","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"He also told investigators","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"that the men","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"who attacked","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"yelled ,","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"`` This is MAGA country , '' a reference to President Donald Trump 's 2016 campaign slogan .","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"Assistant State ' s Attorney Risa Lanier said","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"Smollett plotted the attack with the brothers ,","depth":11},{"id":39,"text":"describing one of the men , Abimbola \" Abel \" Osundairo , 25 , as a close friend of the actor 's .","depth":11},{"id":40,"text":"Three men met on Jan. 25","depth":12},{"id":41,"text":"and planned the attack during a conversation in the actor ' s car .","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"The attack was originally planned for 10 p.m. CST on Jan. 28 ,","depth":12},{"id":43,"text":"but had to be pushed back a few hours","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"because the actor ' s flight from New York was delayed .","depth":13},{"id":45,"text":"Smollett asked the other brother , Olabinjo Osundairo , to `` place a rope around his neck ,","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"pour gasoline on him","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"and yell ,","depth":14},{"id":48,"text":"' This is MAGA country . ' \"","depth":14},{"id":49,"text":"He also initially directed the brothers to pour gasoline on him during the attack","depth":13},{"id":50,"text":"but later suggested","depth":14},{"id":51,"text":"they use bleach ,","depth":14},{"id":52,"text":"Lanier said .","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"Smollett and the brothers met again on Jan. 27 .","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"The actor picked the men up from their home on the city ' s North Side","depth":13},{"id":55,"text":"and drove them to the area near his apartment","depth":14},{"id":56,"text":"where he wanted them to stage the attack .","depth":14},{"id":57,"text":"A witness , an employee of nearby NBC News , saw it all go down .","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"The actor instructed the brothers not to bring their cellphones with them .","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"That day he also wrote a $ 3,500 check to Abel Osundairo","depth":14},{"id":60,"text":"that was backdated to Jan. 23 .","depth":14},{"id":61,"text":"He also gave them $ 100","depth":15},{"id":62,"text":"to buy a ski mask , red hat and other supplies","depth":16},{"id":63,"text":"to be used in the attack ,","depth":16},{"id":64,"text":"Lanier said .","depth":14},{"id":65,"text":"\" Smollett also stated","depth":14},{"id":66,"text":"that he wanted the brothers to catch his attention","depth":15},{"id":67,"text":"by calling him an ' Empire ' F , 'Empire ' N , \"","depth":15},{"id":68,"text":"Lanier said .","depth":13},{"id":69,"text":"\" Smollett further detailed","depth":13},{"id":70,"text":"he wanted Abel to attack him ,","depth":14},{"id":71,"text":"but not hurt him too badly","depth":15},{"id":72,"text":"and give him a chance","depth":16},{"id":73,"text":"to appear to fight back . ''","depth":16},{"id":74,"text":"Prosecutors say","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"texts between Abel Osundairo and Smollett show","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"he also provided the drug ecstasy to the actor .","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"A half dozen people","depth":12},{"id":78,"text":"who were identified to the court as family members of Smollett","depth":12},{"id":79,"text":"watched the roughly 15 minute hearing .","depth":11},{"id":80,"text":"Smollett ,","depth":13},{"id":81,"text":"wearing a light black winter coat ,","depth":13},{"id":82,"text":"watched intently","depth":13},{"id":83,"text":"as Lanier detailed the prosecution ' s case .","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"At moments , his mouth fell slightly agape","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"as Lanier outlined what","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"they think","depth":14},{"id":87,"text":"happened .","depth":14},{"id":88,"text":"Judge Lyke was taken aback by the allegations","depth":12},{"id":89,"text":"outlined against Smollett","depth":12},{"id":90,"text":"even as he told the actor","depth":12},{"id":91,"text":"he has the presumption of innocence .","depth":12},{"id":92,"text":"\" The most vile and despicable part of it ,","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"if it ' s true ,","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"is the noose , ''","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"said Lyke ,","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"who is black .","depth":13},{"id":97,"text":"`` That symbol conjures up such evil in this country ' s history . ''","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"Jack Prior , a member Smollett ' s legal defense team , said","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"his client \" vehemently denies \" the charges","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"and said","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"that the case","depth":13},{"id":102,"text":"presented by prosecutors","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"doesn ' t jibe with the actor ' s character .","depth":12},{"id":104,"text":"He noted","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"that in his five years living in Chicago ,","depth":11},{"id":106,"text":"Smollett has become involved in philanthropy and volunteer work ,","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"even giving song-writing classes to detainees in the Illinois correctional system .","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"Smollett 's defense team","depth":7},{"id":109,"text":"-","depth":8},{"id":110,"text":"which recently added Los Angeles-based celebrity defense lawyer Mark Geragos","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"to assist with the case -","depth":9},{"id":112,"text":"later said in a statement :","depth":6},{"id":113,"text":"\" Today we witnessed an organized law enforcement spectacle","depth":8},{"id":114,"text":"that has no place in the American legal system .","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"The presumption of innocence , a bedrock in the search for justice , was trampled upon at the expense of Mr. Smollett and notably , on the eve of a Mayoral election .","depth":7},{"id":116,"text":"Mr. Smollett is a young man of impeccable character and integrity","depth":7},{"id":117,"text":"who fiercely and solemnly maintains his innocence","depth":8},{"id":118,"text":"and feels betrayed by a system","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"that apparently wants to skip due process","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"and proceed directly to sentencing . \"","depth":10},{"id":121,"text":"At a morning news conference , police detailed","depth":9},{"id":122,"text":"how the 36-year-old actor choreographed the attack in an attempt","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"to raise his profile .","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"Police Superintendent Eddie Johnson ,","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"who is also African-American ,","depth":11},{"id":126,"text":"said","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"Smollett staged the Jan. 29 attack","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"to look like a hate crime ,","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"to take `` advantage of the pain and anger of racism","depth":12},{"id":130,"text":"to promote his career ...","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"because he was dissatisfied with his salary . ''","depth":13},{"id":132,"text":"Smollett has played Jamal Lyon on `` Empire '' since 2015 .","depth":7},{"id":133,"text":"Fox said Thursday","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"it is weighing its response .","depth":9},{"id":135,"text":"\" We understand the seriousness of this matter","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"and we respect the legal process , ''","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"20th Century Fox Studio and Fox Entertainment said in a statement .","depth":10},{"id":138,"text":"`` We are evaluating the situation","depth":10},{"id":139,"text":"and we are considering our options . \"","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"Smollett could face up to one to three years in prison and substantial fines for disorderly conduct , a charge","depth":9},{"id":141,"text":"that `` can mean , say , causing a scene in public , \"","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"Adam Citron , a former New York state prosecutor turned defense attorney said .","depth":10},{"id":143,"text":"\" In Illinois the law prohibits specific acts","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"that waste public resources","depth":11},{"id":145,"text":"or cause unnecessary public fear or stress ,","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"and one of those acts is making a false police report . \"","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"Smollett 's initial status as a crime victim began to shift last weekend","depth":8},{"id":148,"text":"after police arrested and interviewed the Osundairos ,","depth":9},{"id":149,"text":"who were originally identified as suspects","depth":10},{"id":150,"text":"after turning up in surveillance footage .","depth":10},{"id":151,"text":"They were seen running from the area ,","depth":8},{"id":152,"text":"Commander Edward Wodnicki said .","depth":8},{"id":153,"text":"Police learned","depth":10},{"id":154,"text":"that the Osundairos , both U.S. citizens , had flown to Nigeria soon after the attack ,","depth":10},{"id":155,"text":"so officers immediately arrested the men at O'Hare International Airport .","depth":9},{"id":156,"text":"The brothers were held in police custody for nearly two full days , the maximum","depth":10},{"id":157,"text":"police can hold suspects","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"without charging them ,","depth":11},{"id":159,"text":"before they cooperated with investigators .","depth":9},{"id":160,"text":"Their attorney , Gloria Schmidt , told police","depth":9},{"id":161,"text":"the brothers were willing to give a video interview .","depth":9},{"id":162,"text":"\" It was at that time","depth":10},{"id":163,"text":"that this investigation began to spin in an absolutely new direction , \"","depth":10},{"id":164,"text":"Wodnicki said .","depth":9},{"id":165,"text":"Meanwhile , the FBI is also in preliminary stages","depth":8},{"id":166,"text":"of investigating Smollet 's role in the threatening letter","depth":9},{"id":167,"text":"sent to him at the Chicago studio","depth":10},{"id":168,"text":"where `` Empire '' films .","depth":10},{"id":169,"text":"The letter was sent on Jan. 22 , one week before his alleged assault .","depth":7},{"id":170,"text":"He could potentially faced federal charges as well ,","depth":7},{"id":171,"text":"investigators said .","depth":7},{"id":172,"text":"Johnson called on Smollett to come clean .","depth":6},{"id":173,"text":"Police did not immediately have an estimate","depth":8},{"id":174,"text":"for how much was spent","depth":9},{"id":175,"text":"carrying out the investigation .","depth":9},{"id":176,"text":"\" Absolute justice would be an apology to this city","depth":9},{"id":177,"text":"that he smeared ,","depth":9},{"id":178,"text":"admitting what he did","depth":10},{"id":179,"text":"and then be man enough","depth":11},{"id":180,"text":"to offer what he should offer up in terms of all the resources","depth":12},{"id":181,"text":"that were put into this , ''","depth":12},{"id":182,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":183,"text":"More :","depth":3},{"id":184,"text":"Don Lemon weighs in on Jussie Smollett :","depth":4},{"id":185,"text":"'There were credible reasons","depth":5},{"id":186,"text":"to be skeptical '","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":373,"left":0,"right":372,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":372,"left":368,"right":371,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":368,"left":306,"right":367,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":306,"left":293,"right":305,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":293,"left":210,"right":292,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":210,"left":198,"right":209,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":198,"left":189,"right":197,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":189,"left":188,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":188,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":197,"left":196,"right":12,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":196,"left":191,"right":195,"relation":"joi